## Rootstock testnet (development default)
NEXT_PUBLIC_CHAIN_ID=31
NEXT_PUBLIC_RSK_RPC=https://rootstock-testnet.drpc.org
NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=your_walletconnect_project_id_here
# Blockscout explorer API (testnet)
NEXT_PUBLIC_EXPLORER_API=https://rootstock-testnet.blockscout.com/api

# Optional tuning for approval log scanning (keeps RPC load manageable).
# Lower values scan in more chunks (slower, but safer on rate limits).
APPROVAL_SCAN_CHUNK_SIZE=5000

## Rootstock mainnet example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CHAIN_ID=30
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RSK_RPC=https://public-node.rsk.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_EXPLORER_API=https://rootstock.blockscout.com/api